CompileFlags:
  Add:
    - -xc++
    - -Wall
    - -Wpedantic
    - -Wextra
    - -Werror
    - -Wunused-parameter
    - -xcuda
    - --cuda-path=/usr/local/cuda-11
    - --cuda-gpu-arch=sm_86
    - -I/usr/local/cuda-11/include
    - -Iinclude/
    - -Ibenchmarks/include/
    - -lcudart_static
    - -L/usr/local/cuda/lib64
  Compiler: nvcc

Diagnostics:
  ClangTidy:
    Add: [modernize*, clang-diagnostic-*, clang-analyzer-*, cppcoreguidelines-*]
